data.description: This 3BD, 2BA brick ranch offers 1456sf with great curb appeal and front patio! Freshly painted inside with brand new light switches, plates and outlets for that pristine finish! Formal Living Room and large bright Family Rm with patio door to deck! Spacious  Kitchen with pantry and Dining Area! Primary BD has plenty of room and new flooring in the BA! Great closet space in all the bedrooms! Convenient Laundry in hall closet! Large 2car Gar and fenced in big back yard with shed! Updated heating system w/Brand new Electric forced air furnace this year! Central Air and also radiant ceiling heat as a second option. City sewer and well! Septic was filled in! Just move in this beauty and make it yours!
